com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.api

Class JsonEmbedFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.api.EmbedFactory
      • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.api.JsonEmbedFactory

  • public class JsonEmbedFactory
extends EmbedFactory
    This class is similar to EmbedFactory but it uses a EmbedCache to first deserialize the embeds from json and then inject all needed values.
    Since:
    1.1.0
    Version:
    1.1.1
    Author:
    Kaktushose
    See Also:
    EmbedFactory, EmbedCache
